2. Capture Network Traffic

Normal browsing activities and requests to https://192.168.56.102 (FireNetX portal) were generated while capture was active.

Captured protocols included:

DNS: for domain resolution

ARP: for local IP-to-MAC mapping

HTTP/HTTPS: for web traffic

TCP/UDP: transport layer communication

